{"tid":1539992,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不要與極權政府對話 對話=輸","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T06:23:17.000Z","uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2982556ab7a1f3b32a6d31d15096de398e3fe472","tid":1539992,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"陳雲：不要與極權政府建立任何對話關係。Once you do this, you are done.  Once they do this for you, you are done.<br />\n目前，民主派已經召開記者會，與極權政府對話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Px9Ukuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPx9Ukuv.jpg&h=eb274c55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14r3Yga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14r3Yga.jpg&h=bc1c451f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnaXigd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnaXigd.jpg&h=546a8a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgcCige.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgcCige.jpg&h=2ed2c4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3rfPnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3rfPnU.jpg&h=97363e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxEX2HV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxEX2HV.jpg&h=02b73442&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KQPTPC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KQPTPC.png&h=636ebf77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWWLr9D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWWLr9D.png&h=6772b3b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df5ba6970c8b773bdeb6a350e2e104a3fbf0cf4c","tid":1539992,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲廢post<br />\n不推文回覆</